<DOCNO> LA040394-0046 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 028697 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 3, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Magazine; Page 32; Magazine Desk 
</P>
