<DOCNO> LA040394-0066 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 028717 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 3, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
