</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA040394-0183 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 028834 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 3, 1994, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 2; Column 1; Advance Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
