<P>
BLACK DORM'S ONE WHITE RESIDENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 John O'Brien, 21, of Washington, D.C., is the sole white student in Harambee 
House. 
</P>
<P>
 After taking a trip to Kenya and taking African studies, he decided to move 
in. 
</P>
