lectures focusing on the Latino community that include a lecture series, an 
exhibition at USC's Fisher Gallery and acquisition of paintings and sculptures 
for the school's permanent art collection. 
</P>
<P>
 About 12% of the university's 15,000 undergraduate students are Latinos, up 
from 6% in 1988. 
