IRVINE LAW FIRM'S TITLE CHANGE LISTS THE NAMES OF FIVE PARTNERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ernest Brown & Co., a 16-lawyer firm based in Irvine, has announced a name 
change to Brown, Pistone, Hurley, Van Vlear & Seltzer. 
</P>
<P>
 The change, which took effect this week, reflects a desire to give greater 
recognition to the partners, said Ernest C. Brown, managing partner. 
</P>
