</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In last Sunday's cover story on mystery films, the status of "Poodle Springs" 
was mischaracterized. The film is still in development at Universal Studios. 
Also, filming began last month on "Devil in a Blue Dress." 
</P>
